  "id": "jshell-501",
  "name": "JShell 501 — Expert: Data Pipelines & Functional Patterns",
  "description": "Advanced functional programming in Java: custom functional interfaces, method references, function composition, Predicate/BiFunction combinators, parallel streams, and a complete end-to-end analytics pipeline.",
  "created": "2026-03-29T00:00:00",
